content: I don't have information on specific residential towers. however, generally, amenities available to tenants of residential towers may include a fitness center, pool and hot tub, communal outdoor spaces, parking, laundry facilities, 24-hour concierge service, on-site maintenance, and security. some luxury buildings may also offer additional amenities such as a rooftop garden, pet-friendly features, private event spaces, bike storage, and even a restaurant or retail stores on the ground floor.
